main event: A witness observed a strange light in the sky over Fairborn, Ohio.
interesting points: The light was first seen in the west and then turned and headed northwest.
The light flickered and no notice was made.
The report was sent to Project Blue Book, but they did not consider it as being seen from their central office.
The report is listed as conflicting.
The witness stated this was only one of many sightings of strange lights in the Fairborn area.
sighted object: a strange flickering light in the sky
